Leaps of Faith
----------------

Value Proposition Leap of Faith, Proven by: People will actually use our product
-------------------------------
What is our Hypothosis: 
We assume that people want a better way to share the web with close friends

With 10 test groups of X size
	- Solve the network effects & find the people who need this the most.
	- The behaviour we want to see in them after __________________ is ___________________.




- 
- Will they invite a friend to use it with?
	- Can they turn that friend into a user?
- Will they come back day over day
